And you provoke me.

788
00:48:23.467 --> 00:48:26.797
You disrupted the
peace in my own home.

789
00:48:26.821 --> 00:48:29.921
I could snap you like a twig.

790
00:48:32.293 --> 00:48:34.604
Yet I haven't.

791
00:48:34.628 --> 00:48:36.228
Now. why is that?

792
00:48:38.683 --> 00:48:42.179
It's your choice.

793
00:48:42.203 --> 00:48:44.303
Indeed it is.

794
00:48:45.573 --> 00:48:49.203
You're an old
vampire. I can tell.

795
00:48:49.227 --> 00:48:51.338
You've had hundreds of
years to better yourself.

796
00:48:51.362 --> 00:48:53.524
yet you haven't.

797
00:48:53.548 --> 00:48:56.026
You are still a savage.

798
00:48:56.050 --> 00:48:58.595
and I fear for all of us.

799
00:48:58.619 --> 00:49:02.833
humans and vampires.

800
00:49:02.857 --> 00:49:05.169
if this behavior persists.

801
00:49:05.193 --> 00:49:07.421
You.

802
00:49:07.445 --> 00:49:10.413
You seem to know her.

803
00:49:12.283 --> 00:49:14.511
Yes. sheriff.

804
00:49:14.535 --> 00:49:17.552
GODRIC: Escort
her from the nest.

805
00:49:19.073 --> 00:49:21.890
Go ahead. I'm fine.

806
00:49:23.677 --> 00:49:26.390
I wish you out of
my area before dawn.

807
00:49:26.414 --> 00:49:28.414
[♪♪♪]

808
00:49:35.807 --> 00:49:39.787
LORENA: I don't know
how it got this way.

809
00:49:39.811 --> 00:49:42.957
I can't help that
I still love you.

810
00:49:42.981 --> 00:49:45.414
You know I do.

811
00:49:46.951 --> 00:49:50.364
But now it's become

812
00:49:50.388 --> 00:49:53.806
nothing but a
constant humiliation.

813
00:49:57.462 --> 00:50:01.730
The pain that you suffer
you've inflicted upon yourself.

814
00:50:04.685 --> 00:50:08.136
When will we see
each other again?

815
00:50:13.510 --> 00:50:14.704
Never.

816
00:50:14.728 --> 00:50:18.007
We're immortal.

817
00:50:18.031 --> 00:50:21.583
Our paths are bound
to cross eventually.

818
00:50:24.071 --> 00:50:26.333
I have him by the neck. shaking.

819
00:50:26.357 --> 00:50:28.568
But. uh.

820
00:50:28.592 --> 00:50:31.554
it's kind of funny you
say that because...

821
00:50:31.578 --> 00:50:33.578
[♪♪♪]

822
00:50:53.534 --> 00:50:55.779
Luke?

823
00:50:55.803 --> 00:50:57.931
What the fuck. man?

824
00:50:57.955 --> 00:51:00.851
Stay away from me. Stackhouse.
Got nothing to say to you.

825
00:51:00.875 --> 00:51:04.309
What the hell you
doing? Just go.

826
00:51:08.315 --> 00:51:09.715
Excuse me. everyone.

827
00:51:14.622 --> 00:51:16.655
LUKE: If I could
have your attention.

828
00:51:18.259 --> 00:51:21.104
My name is Luke McDonald.

829
00:51:21.128 --> 00:51:23.823
I'm a member of the
Fellowship of the Sun.

830
00:51:23.847 --> 00:51:25.926
and I have a message for you all

831
00:51:25.950 --> 00:51:29.630
from Reverend Steve Newlin.

832
00:51:29.654 --> 00:51:31.565
[BEEPING]

833
00:51:31.589 --> 00:51:32.933
[GASPS]

834
00:51:32.957 --> 00:51:34.956
[♪♪♪]

